        },
        "body": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Every AKINNA piece begins not in a factory, but in the vision of a story waiting to be told. We draw inspiration from architecture, art, and the world around us, shaping a new-age design language that feels modern and global. Each idea then takes form in the hands of master artisans in India, men and women whose skills have been honed over decades and passed down through generations. Rooted in India's rich craft heritage yet expressed through contemporary silhouettes, every handbag becomes more than an accessory; it is a dialogue between tradition and modernity, between precision and poetry.</p>"
          }
        },
