        "body": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>It takes over 28 hours to bring a single AKINNA bag to life, with every stitch, curve, and detail carefully considered to ensure it will be carried, loved, and remembered for years. We are deeply committed to ethical production, supporting skilled artisans and celebrating India's rich craftsmanship. By producing in small batches, we stay true to our values, prioritising quality and precision over mass production, so every creation is as unique and enduring as the person who carries it.</p>"
          }
        },
