        },
        "body": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>At AKINNA, we use only top-grain Indian leathers, each carefully selected for its rich texture, lasting strength, and commitment to ethical sourcing. Every hide tells a story of heritage craftsmanship and mindful production, reflecting our dedication to sustainability. All our leathers are LWG-certified, ensuring that quality and responsibility go hand in hand. Our leather speaks softly, yet stands tall; a reflection of the enduring elegance, meticulous attention to detail, and thoughtful design that defines every AKINNA creation.</p>"
          }
        },
